## Definition of done

- [ ] Adding a new popup requires only one new file, no central edits.
- [ ] Engine returns a single winner per trigger by priority.
- [ ] Every existing condition and its state source is preserved unchanged; no
      conditions added, dropped, or reinterpreted.
- [ ] Any cooldown/seen logic that already existed is consolidated in one place;
      none was invented where it didn't exist.
- [ ] Overlapping triggers cannot double-present; presentation is main-actor.
- [ ] Tests cover winner selection, cooldown, the double-present guard, and
      per-trigger eligibility.
- [ ] Old sequencer decision code is removed.
